#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Enter a branch or tag name to update the AI Assistant plugin from the main repository.\n"
"\n"
"Default: \"main\" (latest development version)\n"
"Examples: \"main\", \"v1.12\", \"v1.11-rc2\"\n"
